        "jsCode": "const now = new Date();\nconst data = $(\"Validate Data\").item.json;\n\nconsole.log(`[${now.toISOString()}] AI Fallback Handler - OpenAI failed, using backup template`);\n\nconst fallbackReport = `Executive Summary\n\nThis week, ${data.client_name} generated $${data.revenue.toLocaleString()} in revenue with a ROAS of ${data.roas}x from $${data.ad_spend.toLocaleString()} in ad spend. Performance ${data.growth_percentage > 0 ? \"increased\" : \"decreased\"} by ${Math.abs(data.growth_percentage)}% compared to the previous week.\n\nKey Wins\n\n- Total revenue: $${data.revenue.toLocaleString()}\n- Return on ad spend: ${data.roas}x\n- Total purchases: ${data.purchases}\n- Top performing campaign: ${data.top_campaign}\n- Best selling product: ${data.best_product}\n\nProblems Detected\n\n${data.roas < 2 ? \"- ROAS is below the 2.0x threshold, indicating lower profitability\\n\" : \"\"}${data.growth_percentage < -20 ? \"- Revenue declined significantly compared to last week\\n\" : \"\"}${data.roas >= 2 && data.growth_percentage >= -20 ? \"- No critical issues detected this week\\n\" : \"\"}\nRecommendations\n\n1. Review and optimize underperforming campaigns\n2. Increase budget allocation to top-performing campaigns\n3. Test new ad creatives and messaging\n4. Analyze customer feedback and reviews\n5. Monitor competitor activities and market trends\n\nGrowth Opportunities\n\n- Scale successful campaigns with proven ROAS\n- Expand product offerings based on best sellers\n- Implement retargeting strategies for cart abandoners\n- Explore new marketing channels and platforms\n- Optimize landing pages for higher conversion rates`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    ...data,\n    choices: [{ message: { content: fallbackReport } }]\n  }\n}];"
